{
  "id": "RAW_afc30fde",
  "title": "我们该如何看待 Anthropic 关于 Mythos 那份（可能）令人恐惧的新报告？",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/what-should-we-take-from-anthropics",
  "date": "2026-04-08 17:47:38",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\">\n   <p><span>Everybody’s talking about Anthropic’s new but unreleased model </span><a href=\"https://red.anthropic.com/2026/mythos-preview/\" rel>Mythos</a><span> (and the related </span><a href=\"https://www.anthropic.com/glasswing\" rel>Project Glasswing</a><span>) and how it might undermine or even devastate cybersecurity. There are a lot of ostensibly terrifying reports about Mythos, like this one:</span></p>\n   <a href=\"https://x.com/jimvandehei/status/2041817666881503351?s=61\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n    <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/jimvandehei/status/2041817666881503351?s=61&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;This is the scary phase of AI — a model deemed so powerful that its full release into the wild could unleash untold catastrophe. \\n🚨Based on our conversations with government and private-sector officials briefed on Mythos, this isn't hyperbole. It's reality.&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;JimVandeHei&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Jim VandeHei&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1483401483408351236/XDH840G8_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-04-08T09:57:21.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{},&quot;reply_count&quot;:15,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:103,&quot;like_count&quot;:188,&quot;impression_count&quot;:79798,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n      <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n       <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n        <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XDH840G8.jpg 40w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!0fLd!,w_80,h_80,c_fill,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.substack.com%2Fprofile_images%2F1483401483408351236%2FXDH840G8.jpg 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XDH840G8.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"40px\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XDH840G8.jpg\" sizes=\"40px\" alt=\"X avatar for @JimVandeHei\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XDH840G8.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XDH840G8.jpg 80w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fbe504ce-beac-4435-a2e4-dda4b4d55300/public 120w\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Jim VandeHei</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@JimVandeHei</span>\n      </div>\n      <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n       <g>\n        <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n       </g>\n      </svg>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">This is the scary phase of AI — a model deemed so powerful that its full release into the wild could unleash untold catastrophe. 🚨Based on our conversations with government and private-sector officials briefed on Mythos, this isn't hyperbole. It's reality.</div>\n     <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">9:57 AM · Apr 8, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">79.8K Views</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n       <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">15 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">103 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">188 Likes</span>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div> \n   </a>\n   <p><span>Tom Friedman </span><a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/07/opinion/anthropic-ai-claude-mythos.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share\" rel>panicked about it in the NYT</a><span>, too.</span></p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c51cb06a-761d-4802-6ade-97c545677a00/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b03d13a2-78b4-4083-2d23-6838a5a1c400/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4192d07d-4ef9-42cb-caa5-0fa791d2fa00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png\" width=\"1268\" height=\"293\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:293,&quot;width&quot;:1268,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:47178,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/193591131?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/48c0601c-ebba-48fe-2571-3ebd02337400/public 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/03c7222b-f1fd-49be-990a-d946ddc28f00/public 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_069863f4-c5c8-4fb2-a5c7-38f97862705c_1268x293.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <p>Since I haven’t gotten to play with Mythos (which has not been public released), there’s a lot I don’t know, but here are a few bets:</p>\n   <ol>\n    <li>\n     <p><span>It’s </span><em>probably</em><span> not as bad as they say, as AI and cybersecurity expert Heidy Khlaaf explains in this thread, which I highly recommend:</span></p>\n     <a href=\"https://x.com/HeidyKhlaaf/status/2041591737563394442?s=20\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-component-name=\"Twitter2ToDOM\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset\"> \n      <div data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://x.com/HeidyKhlaaf/status/2041591737563394442?s=20&quot;,&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;As someone who has audited dozens of safety-critical systems, built static analysis tools, and used most formal verification and security tools, here are some red flags that should be a caution in taking these claims at face value:\\n1. There are no comparison benchmarks with 1/&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;HeidyKhlaaf&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Dr Heidy Khlaaf (هايدي خلاف)&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/2009948381561364480/ojJeiReo_normal.jpg&quot;,&quot;date&quot;:&quot;2026-04-07T18:59:35.000Z&quot;,&quot;photos&quot;:[],&quot;quoted_tweet&quot;:{&quot;full_text&quot;:&quot;Introducing Project Glasswing: an urgent initiative to help secure the world’s most critical software.\\n\\nIt’s powered by our newest frontier model, Claude Mythos Preview, which can find software vulnerabilities better than all but the most skilled humans.\\nhttps://t.co/NQ7IfEtYk7&quot;,&quot;username&quot;:&quot;AnthropicAI&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Anthropic&quot;,&quot;profile_image_url&quot;:&quot;https://pbs.substack.com/profile_images/1798110641414443008/XP8gyBaY_normal.jpg&quot;},&quot;reply_count&quot;:46,&quot;retweet_count&quot;:132,&quot;like_count&quot;:1525,&quot;impression_count&quot;:531935,&quot;expanded_url&quot;:null,&quot;video_url&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false}\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-12 pc-padding-16 pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-md sizing-border-box-DggLA4 pressable-lg-kV7yq8 font-text-qe4AeH tweet-fWkQfo twitter-embed\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-12 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n        <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n         <div style=\"--scale:40px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-40 pc-height-40 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n          <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_ojJeiReo.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_ojJeiReo.jpg 80w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_ojJeiReo.jpg 120w\" sizes=\"40px\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_ojJeiReo.jpg\" sizes=\"40px\" alt=\"X avatar for @HeidyKhlaaf\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_ojJeiReo.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_ojJeiReo.jpg 80w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ce9935f5-cb79-4886-ee13-6a13e9252100/public 120w\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-reset flex-grow-rzmknG\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Dr Heidy Khlaaf (هايدي خلاف)</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@HeidyKhlaaf</span>\n        </div>\n        <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px;\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke=\"#000\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n         <g>\n          <title></title><path stroke=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M13.2879 19.1666L8.66337 12.575L2.87405 19.1666H0.424805L7.57674 11.0258L0.424805 0.833252H6.71309L11.0717 7.04577L16.5327 0.833252H18.982L12.1619 8.59699L19.5762 19.1666H13.2879ZM16.0154 17.3083H14.3665L3.93176 2.69159H5.58092L9.7601 8.54422L10.4828 9.55981L16.0154 17.3083Z\"></path>\n         </g>\n        </svg>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">As someone who has audited dozens of safety-critical systems, built static analysis tools, and used most formal verification and security tools, here are some red flags that should be a caution in taking these claims at face value: 1. There are no comparison benchmarks with 1/</div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset elevatedTheme-fBklGV\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-padding-12 pc-boxShadow-none pc-reset bg-primary-zk6FDl outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-sm sizing-border-box-DggLA4\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-row pc-gap-8 pc-alignItems-center pc-reset\">\n          <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n           <div style=\"--scale:20px;\" title=\"User\" class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-width-20 pc-height-20 pc-justifyContent-center pc-alignItems-center pc-position-relative pc-reset bg-secondary-UUD3_J flex-auto-j3S2WA outline-detail-vcQLyr pc-borderRadius-full overflow-hidden-WdpwT6 sizing-border-box-DggLA4 container-TAtrWj\">\n            <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XP8gyBaY.jpg 20w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5b87c0d0-740c-444e-6964-1123b2ab4a00/public 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XP8gyBaY.jpg 60w\" sizes=\"20px\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XP8gyBaY.jpg\" sizes=\"20px\" alt=\"X avatar for @AnthropicAI\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XP8gyBaY.jpg 20w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XP8gyBaY.jpg 40w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_XP8gyBaY.jpg 60w\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" draggable=\"false\" class=\"img-OACg1c object-fit-cover-u4ReeV pencraft pc-reset\"></picture>\n           </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n           <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset weight-semibold-uqA4FV reset-IxiVJZ\">Anthropic</span> <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s reset-IxiVJZ\">@AnthropicAI</span>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-15-Psle70 weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ text-aFN1BV\">Introducing Project Glasswing: an urgent initiative to help secure the world’s most critical software. It’s powered by our newest frontier model, Claude Mythos Preview, which can find software vulnerabilities better than all but the most skilled humans. https://t.co/NQ7IfEtYk7</div>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-flexDirection-column pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">6:59 PM · Apr 7, 2026</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">532K Views</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-reset color-secondary-ls1g8s line-height-20-t4M0El font-text-qe4AeH size-13-hZTUKr weight-regular-mUq6Gb reset-IxiVJZ\">\n         <span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">46 Replies</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">132 Reposts</span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\"> · </span><span class=\"pencraft pc-reset reset-IxiVJZ\">1.53K Likes</span>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n     <p>As a cybersecurity friend said to me in a text: “I haven’t had time to go through all of the write-ups yet, but it smells overhyped to me. Oh, we have this powerful model, but you can’t evaluate it yourself. I don’t doubt some of the results, but what’s made of it and the conditions under which the vulnerabilities were found, and what role humans played, isn’t clear… To me, the conditions and the scenarios are what matter. My gut tells me that if they released it publicly, we’d have some advancements but far from the exponential benefits they seem to be implying. It seems to me they are planting seeds in the hype garden.”</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span>Whether or not Mythos is AGI per se is a red herring. (It probably isn’t; it’s telling that the report says very little about overall capabilities.) Crucially, </span><strong>AI doesn’t need to be AGI to cause harm</strong><span>! </span><a href=\"https://gizmodo.com/sam-altman-says-itll-take-another-year-before-chatgpt-can-start-a-timer-2000743487\" rel>ChatGPT can’t reliably run a timer</a><span> but it has still been implicated in delusions, suicides, cognitive surrender, mass disinformation, and so much more. Mythos may wreak havoc even if it hallucinates and lacks reliability outside of domains like coding and math. A system doesn’t have to be AGI to carry risks. </span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span>The strongest lesson here is about policy. Anthropic showed some admirable restraint in not publicly releasing a potentially dangerous technology.</span><span style=\"min-width:0;\" data-state=\"closed\"><a data-component-name=\"FootnoteAnchorToDOM\" id=\"footnote-anchor-1-193591131\" href=\"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/what-should-we-take-from-anthropics#footnote-1-193591131\" target=\"_self\" rel class=\"footnote-anchor\">1</a></span><span> But some of their competitors (such as OpenAI and xAI) might well not. Whether Mythos is as scary as it sounds or not, the reality is that without any government oversight on what can be released, we are entirely at the mercy of individual CEOs, some of whom have decidedly not earned our trust. </span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p>Corollary, as pointed out to me by a friend who read a draft of this essay, “it is impossible to disentangle real concerns from fear mongering being used as a marketing strategy, and so it just is not possible to separate justified panic from mere advertising which is why we need government oversight!”</p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span>What about China? We need an international agency and treaty. That’s what I have been arguing all along. That was </span><em>the </em><span>point of my </span><a href=\"https://www.ted.com/talks/gary_marcus_the_urgent_risks_of_runaway_ai_and_what_to_do_about_them\" rel>2023 TED talk</a><span> and 2023 invited essay with Anka Reuel in </span><a href=\"https://www.economist.com/by-invitation/2023/04/18/the-world-needs-an-international-agency-for-artificial-intelligence-say-two-ai-experts\" rel>The Economist</a><span>. We still do. Mythos (and the </span><a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2026/04/13/sam-altman-may-control-our-future-can-he-be-trusted\" rel>reporting around Altman</a><span>) only make that clearer. Self-regulation is too little, too late. </span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p>The situation is this: three years of self-serving and misleading arguments about how regulation would allegedly preclude innovation has left us up shit’s creek, without a paddle.</p>\n   <p><span>I can’t tell </span><em>exactly</em><span> how far Mythos (or similar competitive systems that will no doubt follow) leave us up that creek, but I do know that the time for crafting paddles is running out.</span></p>\n   <div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\">\n    <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\">\n     <div class=\"container-IpPqBD\">\n      <form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" novalidate class=\"form form-M5sC90\">\n       <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\">\n       <div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\">\n        <div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\">\n         <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative pc-reset flex-auto-j3S2WA\">\n          <input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\">\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"submit\" disabled class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\"><span class=\"button-text \">Subscribe</span></button>\n       </div>\n      </form>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p>PS. It is worth rereading this warning I issued in January 2025, when asked by Politico for a black swan prediction:</p>\n   <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n    <figure>\n     <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img can-restack\"> \n      <div class=\"image2-inset can-restack\">\n       <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183446_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183446_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1878\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1878,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:423996,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/193591131?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 424w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183446_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260408183445_2c0d730a-056e-484c-99ef-26dfe06851a4_1668x2152.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture>\n       <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n        <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n          <svg role=\"img\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n           <g>\n            <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n           </g>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n         <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n          <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n           <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n          </svg>\n         </button>\n        </div>\n       </div>\n      </div> \n     </a>\n    </figure>\n   </div>\n   <div data-component-name=\"FootnoteToDOM\" class=\"footnote\">\n    <a id=\"footnote-1-193591131\" href=\"https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/what-should-we-take-from-anthropics#footnote-anchor-1-193591131\" contenteditable=\"false\" target=\"_self\" rel class=\"footnote-number\">1</a>\n    <div class=\"footnote-content\">\n     <p>Anthropic also announced a big consortium, partly supported by their financial support, to work on cybersecurity, which is likely a good thing, though one that should work in conjunction with law enforcement and regulation.</p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Gary Marcus 分析了围绕 Anthropic 未发布的 Mythos 模型所产生的炒作，认为尽管其网络安全风险可能被夸大了，但这种情况凸显了政府监管的紧迫性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Gary Marcus 分析了围绕 Anthropic 未发布的 Mythos 模型所产生的炒作，认为尽管其网络安全风险可能被夸大了，但这种情况凸显了政府监管的紧迫性。",
  "summary": "本文探讨了公众对 Anthropic 的 Mythos 模型和 Project Glasswing 的强烈反应，据报道这些模型具备显著的网络安全能力。作者 Gary Marcus 提出了怀疑的观点，认为该模型的能力可能被作为一种营销策略或“炒作花园”而过度宣传。然而，他强调 AI 无需达到 AGI 水平也可能带来危险。核心论点是对行业自我监管的批判；Marcus 认为，此类模型的保密性和潜在风险证明，仅依赖科技公司 CEO 的判断是不足够的，必须通过国际条约和政府监管来管理 AI 的社会影响。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Mythos 的网络安全风险很可能被夸大了，且缺乏透明的基准测试。",
      "explanation": "Marcus 引用专家观点指出，由于缺乏对比基准，且在没有公开访问权限的情况下难以验证 Anthropic 的说法，这表明“可怕”的叙事可能部分源于营销手段。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 系统无需达到 AGI 即可造成重大的现实危害。",
      "explanation": "即使是会产生幻觉的不可靠系统，也可能导致大规模的虚假信息传播或认知投降；过度关注模型是否达到“AGI”反而分散了对其即时风险的注意力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "缺乏政府监管使得公共安全完全受制于个别 CEO 的意愿。",
      "explanation": "虽然 Anthropic 通过不发布 Mythos 展示了克制，但竞争对手未必会这样做，这凸显了自我监管的失败，以及建立国际机构和条约的必要性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我们无法将真正的担忧与作为营销策略的恐慌营销区分开来。",
    "AI 无需达到 AGI 也能造成伤害！",
    "无论 Mythos 是否像听起来那么可怕，现实是，在没有任何政府监管的情况下，我们完全受制于个别 CEO 的判断。",
    "三年来，关于监管会阻碍创新的自私且误导性的论调，已经让我们陷入了进退两难的困境。"
  ],
